Class GenericMeal

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fluffy_minions.prototype.IDAS.GenericMeal
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Breakfast, Dinner, Lunch

    public abstract class GenericMeal
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides the requirements of one meal (breakfast/lunch/dinner), the amount of ingredients that each food contains and the rows in the database.
